summary: Is it odd to say that RIGHT after drawing @kingdomofkitten teenage Ikari, I also thought of what his potential friends would be...
body:
Is it odd to say that RIGHT after drawing @kingdomofkitten teenage Ikari, I also thought of what his potential friends would be like? No? Okay…

On the left is Kuuma, a bear who’s basically a fat otaku. Loves Tokusatsu and spends his money on Toku toys, best girl figurines and Gunpla. He’s sort like the Manumaru to Ikari’s Resasuke… you know what I mean.

On the right is Nezumi, a hedgehog who serves as Ikari’s Fenneko, even the social media detective stuff, only Nezumi takes a step further by resorting to use some of her findings to blackmail others, if she feels the need to. She also has an adult brother named Haru. If you don’t get it, ‘Harunezumi’ is Japanese for ‘hedgehog.’

So yeah, I got more excited about the idea and now more ideas are just rolling out, might even make other classmates, his sempais, and his teacher.
